Our Discord server is a casual, non-judgmental space focused on helping newcomers and sharing modding knowledge.
\n\n
You&#39;ll be joining &lt;b&gt;10,000+&lt;/b&gt; other users. Ask questions, lurk, or track the progress of the modpack. whatever works for you.
	</description>
	<iconPath>Tutor/Discord</iconPath>
	<dimensions>(988, 620)</dimensions>
	<orientationStyle>Right</orientationStyle>
	<closeable>false</closeable>
	<oneTime>true</oneTime>
